.TH mcdecrypt 1
.SH NAME
mcdecrypt \- decrypt ciphertext and recover message
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mcdecrypt <ciphertext 8<secretkey >message
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B mcdecrypt
decrypts a ciphertext
.B ciphertext
using secretkey
.B secretkey
and recovers message
.B message
.sp
.B mcdecrypt
uses post-quantum cryptographic algorithms
.B mceliece8192128
(public-key decryption),
.B chacha20
(symmetric decryption),
.B poly1305
(symmetric authentication),
.B SHA512
(hash)
.SH EXAMPLE
.nf
umask 077
mckeypair 5>pk 9>sk
echo "ahoj" | mcencrypt 4<pk | mcdecrypt 8<sk
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR mckeypair (1),
.BR mcencrypt (1),
.BR https://libpqcrypto.org/command.html
